<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-41-0878 </DOCNO><TEXT>In 1984, the International Solid Wastes and Public Cleansing Association(I.S.W.A.) approved the formation of an international working group onhazardous wastes. This book contains the edited final reports of thetwelve national organisations which formed this working group. Also includedis a review and assessment of various national policies and programsfor waste management, together with recommendations and suggested strategiesfor the future.</TEXT></DOC>